<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>C. M.</author>
<hymn_number>85</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
 Chi Shilombish achukma
 Pi nukfoka pullakbano;
 Il aiahni fehnʋshke.

[V2]
 Chisʋs pulla fehna hocha
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke;
 Nanta'k ocha yʋmohma wa,
 Il i̱ yimmi pullashke.

[V3]
 Chihowa holitopa ma!
 Chiso fehna pia kʋt,
 Aiokpuloka fehna ka
 E chukowa̱ hosishke.

[V4]
 Et ish pi okchalinchashke;
 Ai ilbʋshʋt pillishke;
 Pi̱ki ma! chi̱ hina hanta
 Ish pi fohki pullashke.

[V5]
 Chisʋs chia fehna kak o̱
 Chimmi pia fehnʋshke;
 Ish ai ahanta fehna ka
 Pisht ish ona pullashke.

[V6]
 Chisʋs chia pulla kak o̱
 E chi anukchetoshke;
 Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke,
 Na̱ pi Okchalinchi ma!</lyrics>
<title>Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! ƲIT85</title>
<time_sig>8.7.8.7.</time_sig>
</song>